# API Specification for External Access & MCP Integration

## OpenAPI 3.0 Specification

```yaml
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: German Guitar Marketplace API
  description: |
    RESTful API for the German Guitar Marketplace platform.
    Designed for external integrations and AI-powered MCP access.
  version: "1.0.0"
  contact:
    name: API Support
    email: api@guitar-marketplace.de
  license:
    name: MIT
    url: https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT

servers:
  - url: https://api.guitar-marketplace.de/v1
    description: Production server
  - url: https://staging-api.guitar-marketplace.de/v1
    description: Staging server
  - url: http://localhost:3000/api/v1
    description: Development server

security:
  - BearerAuth: []
  - ApiKeyAuth: []

paths:
  # Public Endpoints (No Authentication Required)
  /health:
    get:
      summary: Health Check
      description: Check API health status
      tags: [System]
      security: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: API is healthy
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HealthResponse'

  /listings:
    get:
      summary: Get Guitar Listings
      description: Retrieve paginated list of active guitar listings
      tags: [Listings]
      security: []
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Page'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Limit'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Search'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Brand'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/GuitarType'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Condition'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/PriceMin'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/PriceMax'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Location'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Sort'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List of guitar listings
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingsResponse'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '500':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/InternalError'

    post:
      summary: Create Guitar Listing
      description: Create a new guitar listing (requires authentication)
      tags: [Listings]
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateListingRequest'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Listing created successfully
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingResponse'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Forbidden'
        '422':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/ValidationError'

  /listings/{listingId}:
    get:
      summary: Get Single Listing
      description: Get detailed information about a specific listing
      tags: [Listings]
      security: []
      parameters:
        - name: listingId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Listing details
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/DetailedListingResponse'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'

    put:
      summary: Update Listing
      description: Update an existing listing (owner only)
      tags: [Listings]
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: listingId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/UpdateListingRequest'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Listing updated successfully
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingResponse'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Forbidden'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'

  /search:
    get:
      summary: Advanced Search
      description: Perform advanced search with AI-powered recommendations
      tags: [Search]
      security: []
      parameters:
        - name: q
          in: query
          description: Search query
          schema:
            type: string
            maxLength: 100
        - name: semantic
          in: query
          description: Enable semantic search
          schema:
            type: boolean
            default: false
        - name: recommendations
          in: query
          description: Include AI recommendations
          schema:
            type: boolean
            default: false
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Search results with optional recommendations
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SearchResponse'

  /recommendations/{userId}:
    get:
      summary: Get User Recommendations
      description: Get personalized recommendations for authenticated user
      tags: [Recommendations]
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: userId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
        - name: type
          in: query
          description: Type of recommendations
          schema:
            type: string
            enum: [similar, trending, personalized]
            default: personalized
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Personalized recommendations
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/RecommendationsResponse'

  # Analytics & Insights (For MCP Integration)
  /analytics/trends:
    get:
      summary: Market Trends
      description: Get current market trends and insights
      tags: [Analytics]
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: timeframe
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            enum: [24h, 7d, 30d, 90d]
            default: 30d
        - name: category
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            enum: [electric, acoustic, bass, classical]
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Market trends data
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TrendsResponse'

  /analytics/price-insights:
    get:
      summary: Price Insights
      description: Get price analysis and market insights
      tags: [Analytics]
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: brand
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: model
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: condition
          in: query
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConditionEnum'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Price insights
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PriceInsightsResponse'

  # AI-Powered Endpoints (For MCP)
  /ai/analyze-listing:
    post:
      summary: Analyze Listing
      description: AI analysis of listing quality and suggestions
      tags: [AI]
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/AnalyzeListingRequest'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Listing analysis results
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingAnalysisResponse'

  /ai/moderate-content:
    post:
      summary: Content Moderation
      description: AI-powered content moderation
      tags: [AI]
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ModerateContentRequest'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Moderation results
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ModerationResponse'

components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
      description: JWT token from Supabase authentication
    
    ApiKeyAuth:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: X-API-Key
      description: API key for external integrations

  parameters:
    Page:
      name: page
      in: query
      description: Page number (1-based)
      schema:
        type: integer
        minimum: 1
        default: 1
    
    Limit:
      name: limit
      in: query
      description: Items per page
      schema:
        type: integer
        minimum: 1
        maximum: 100
        default: 20
    
    Search:
      name: search
      in: query
      description: Search query
      schema:
        type: string
        maxLength: 100
    
    Brand:
      name: brand
      in: query
      description: Filter by guitar brand
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarBrand'
    
    GuitarType:
      name: guitar_type
      in: query
      description: Filter by guitar type
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarType'
    
    Condition:
      name: condition
      in: query
      description: Filter by condition
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConditionEnum'
    
    PriceMin:
      name: price_min
      in: query
      description: Minimum price in EUR
      schema:
        type: number
        minimum: 0
    
    PriceMax:
      name: price_max
      in: query
      description: Maximum price in EUR
      schema:
        type: number
        minimum: 0
    
    Location:
      name: location
      in: query
      description: Filter by location
      schema:
        type: string
        maxLength: 100
    
    Sort:
      name: sort
      in: query
      description: Sort order
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [created_at_desc, created_at_asc, price_desc, price_asc, title_asc, distance_asc]
        default: created_at_desc

  schemas:
    # Core Entities
    GuitarListing:
      type: object
      required: [id, title, description, brand, guitar_type, condition, price, seller_id, status]
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          description: Unique listing identifier
        title:
          type: string
          minLength: 10
          maxLength: 100
          description: Listing title
        description:
          type: string
          minLength: 50
          maxLength: 2000
          description: Detailed description
        brand:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarBrand'
        model:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
          nullable: true
        series:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
          nullable: true
        year:
          type: integer
          minimum: 1900
          maximum: 2030
          nullable: true
        guitar_type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarType'
        condition:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConditionEnum'
        price:
          type: number
          minimum: 50
          maximum: 50000
          multipleOf: 0.01
        price_negotiable:
          type: boolean
          default: false
        images:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            format: uri
          minItems: 1
          maxItems: 10
        location_city:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
        location_state:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
          nullable: true
        shipping_available:
          type: boolean
          default: true
        shipping_cost:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 500
          nullable: true
        pickup_available:
          type: boolean
          default: true
        tags:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            maxLength: 30
          maxItems: 10
        seller_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        status:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingStatus'
        created_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        updated_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        views:
          type: integer
          minimum: 0
        favorites_count:
          type: integer
          minimum: 0

    GuitarBrand:
      type: string
      enum: 
        - Fender
        - Gibson
        - Martin
        - Taylor
        - Ibanez
        - ESP
        - Yamaha
        - PRS
        - Rickenbacker
        - Gretsch
        - Epiphone
        - Squier
        - Jackson
        - Schecter
        - Washburn
        - Dean
        - BC Rich
        - Charvel
        - Kramer
        - Other

    GuitarType:
      type: string
      enum:
        - electric
        - acoustic
        - classical
        - bass
        - hollow_body
        - semi_hollow
        - twelve_string
        - baritone
        - travel
        - resonator

    ConditionEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - mint
        - excellent
        - very_good
        - good
        - fair
        - poor
        - for_parts

    ListingStatus:
      type: string
      enum:
        - draft
        - active
        - pending
        - sold
        - expired
        - removed
        - reported

    # API Responses
    HealthResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [healthy]
        timestamp:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        version:
          type: string

    ListingsResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
        pagination:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PaginationMeta'
        total_count:
          type: integer

    ListingResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'

    DetailedListingResponse:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingResponse'
        - type: object
          properties:
            seller:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PublicProfile'
            similar_listings:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
              maxItems: 5

    SearchResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
        query:
          type: string
        filters_applied:
          type: object
        recommendations:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
          nullable: true
        pagination:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PaginationMeta'

    RecommendationsResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
        recommendation_type:
          type: string
          enum: [similar, trending, personalized]
        confidence_score:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 1

    TrendsResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        timeframe:
          type: string
        trending_brands:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              brand:
                type: string
              count:
                type: integer
              growth_rate:
                type: number
        average_prices:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: number
        market_insights:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string

    PriceInsightsResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        market_value:
          type: object
          properties:
            min:
              type: number
            max:
              type: number
            average:
              type: number
            median:
              type: number
        price_trend:
          type: string
          enum: [increasing, decreasing, stable]
        similar_listings:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarListing'
        recommendations:
          type: object
          properties:
            suggested_price:
              type: number
            confidence:
              type: number

    ListingAnalysisResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        quality_score:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 100
        suggestions:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              category:
                type: string
                enum: [images, description, pricing, title]
              message:
                type: string
              priority:
                type: string
                enum: [low, medium, high]
        market_position:
          type: string
          enum: [underpriced, fairly_priced, overpriced]
        estimated_interest:
          type: string
          enum: [low, medium, high]

    ModerationResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        flagged:
          type: boolean
        categories:
          type: object
          properties:
            harassment:
              type: boolean
            hate:
              type: boolean
            sexual:
              type: boolean
            violence:
              type: boolean
            spam:
              type: boolean
        confidence_scores:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: number
        action_required:
          type: string
          enum: [none, review, remove]

    # Request Schemas
    CreateListingRequest:
      type: object
      required: [title, description, brand, guitar_type, condition, price, location_city, images]
      properties:
        title:
          type: string
          minLength: 10
          maxLength: 100
        description:
          type: string
          minLength: 50
          maxLength: 2000
        brand:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarBrand'
        model:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
        year:
          type: integer
          minimum: 1900
          maximum: 2030
        guitar_type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/GuitarType'
        condition:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ConditionEnum'
        price:
          type: number
          minimum: 50
          maximum: 50000
        price_negotiable:
          type: boolean
        images:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            format: uri
          minItems: 1
          maxItems: 10
        location_city:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
        location_state:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
        shipping_available:
          type: boolean
        shipping_cost:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
        pickup_available:
          type: boolean
        tags:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string

    UpdateListingRequest:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateListingRequest'
        - type: object
          properties:
            status:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListingStatus'

    AnalyzeListingRequest:
      type: object
      required: [listing_data]
      properties:
        listing_data:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateListingRequest'
        include_market_analysis:
          type: boolean
          default: true
        include_suggestions:
          type: boolean
          default: true

    ModerateContentRequest:
      type: object
      required: [content, content_type]
      properties:
        content:
          type: string
        content_type:
          type: string
          enum: [listing_title, listing_description, message, review]
        user_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid

    # Utility Schemas
    PaginationMeta:
      type: object
      properties:
        page:
          type: integer
        limit:
          type: integer
        total_pages:
          type: integer
        total_count:
          type: integer
        has_next:
          type: boolean
        has_previous:
          type: boolean

    PublicProfile:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        username:
          type: string
        avatar_url:
          type: string
          format: uri
          nullable: true
        verification_status:
          type: string
          enum: [unverified, email_verified, phone_verified, identity_verified, fully_verified]
        seller_rating:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 5
        total_sales:
          type: integer
        location:
          type: string
        member_since:
          type: string
          format: date-time

    Error:
      type: object
      required: [error, message]
      properties:
        error:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
        details:
          type: object
        timestamp:
          type: string
          format: date-time

  responses:
    BadRequest:
      description: Bad request
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

    Unauthorized:
      description: Unauthorized
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

    Forbidden:
      description: Forbidden - insufficient permissions
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

    NotFound:
      description: Resource not found
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

    ValidationError:
      description: Validation error
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            allOf:
              - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
              - type: object
                properties:
                  validation_errors:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        field:
                          type: string
                        message:
                          type: string

    InternalError:
      description: Internal server error
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'

# Rate Limiting
x-rate-limit:
  public_endpoints: "100 requests per minute"
  authenticated_endpoints: "200 requests per minute"
  ai_endpoints: "50 requests per minute"

# API Keys for External Access
x-api-access:
  public_data: "No API key required"
  user_data: "JWT authentication required"
  analytics_data: "API key required"
  ai_features: "Premium API key required"
```

## MCP Integration Schema

This API specification is designed to be consumed by MCP servers, enabling AI systems to:

1. **Access Market Data**: Get listings, trends, and analytics
2. **Perform Analysis**: Use AI endpoints for content analysis and moderation
3. **Generate Insights**: Access recommendation and pricing data
4. **Integrate Seamlessly**: Standard REST API with OpenAPI documentation

## External Platform Integration

External platforms can integrate using:
- **REST API**: Standard HTTP endpoints
- **Webhook Events**: Real-time notifications
- **GraphQL**: Advanced querying capabilities (future)
- **SDK Libraries**: JavaScript, Python, etc. (future)

This specification ensures both human developers and AI systems can effectively interact with your platform.